title: Siberia Parking
description:
RUSSIAN GAME

Siberia, snow, military base. You are transporting military equipment to repair.

The harsh Siberian weather, snow. Several trucks. This parking lot is more difficult with a trailer. Different characteristics of tractors, ride on control points on a military base. Russian bear can do anything!
Walk 20 missions on different tractors, show everyone how much you're cool! Soul Plane background music and a lot of snow, if you miss the winter and you love big cars - this game is for you.

- Small game size
- No in-game purchases
- No banners in gameplay
